title: Star Wars Alien Necropsy, Part 1
itunes:title: Star Wars Alien Necropsy, Part 1
description:
In celebration of May the 4th, this episode of Stuff to Blow Your Mind ventures into a galaxy far, far away while also considering the science and biology of our home world. Join Robert and Joe as they break down six fantastic alien species from the Star Wars universe.
